---
title: Spicy Green Salsa Beef Taco Bar Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: Prep, sizzle, zap, serve: Four easy steps to our fastest, freshest weeknight meal yet. Thanks to a few clever time-savers from our chefs, you and yours will belly up to your own taco bar in just 15 minutes! You’ll brown ground beef with green pepper, scallions, and tangy green salsa, then warm refried beans and tortillas and set out all the fixins: pico de gallo, Monterey Jack cheese, guac, and blue corn tortilla chips. Everyone can build their own fresh, flavorful dinner in a flash!
